# Files copied into each git worktree Claude Code creates for an isolated Work Unit.
# .gitignore syntax; only files that match AND are gitignored are copied (tracked
# files are never duplicated). Used when cc_features.worktree_isolation is active.
#
# Env files an isolated WU implementer needs (a worktree is a fresh checkout, so
# untracked .env* are absent unless listed here):
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Cross-WU coherence context the orchestrator writes and subsequent WU
# implementers read (git-ignored per §2.7a, so it needs explicit copy-in):
.tl-telar/context/project-context.md
